title: You'll Never Believe What Happened At This Retirement Home!
description:
Last week, a listener heard us talking about a retirement community in Florida that is WILD. Our listener also happened to work in a retirement community, and she's witnessed some crazy things!
She offered to share her stories…so today, we’re debuting our new SENIOR CITIZEN SOAP OPERA!
